Ellis and back when I was with Dinah.", "doc_title": "Keter Betts interviewed by Monk Rowe, Sarasota, Florida, April 11, 1996", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/keter-betts-interviewed-monk-rowe-sarasota-florida-april-11-1996"}, {"speaker": "Wayne Shorter", "relation": "played with", "confidence": 1.0, "evidence": "I was with Ray Brown one time. I played one job with him at the Russian River Festival.", "doc_title": "Wayne Shorter — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://amhistory.si.edu/jazz/Shorter-Wayne/Shorter_Wayne_Interview_Transcription.pdf"}, {"speaker": "Bob Haggart", "relation": "has met", "confidence": 1.0, "evidence": "when I met Ray Brown he was playing with Dizzy Gillespie’s big band on 52nd street.", "doc_title": "Bob Haggart interviewed by Michael Woods, Clinton, New York, September 22, 1995", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/bob-haggart-interviewed-michael-woods-clinton-new-york-september-22-1995"}]}